1
00:00:03,254 --> 00:00:05,507
<i>Within the spreading darkness</i>

2
00:00:05,590 --> 00:00:08,218
<i>I pledged a vow to the revolution</i>

3
00:00:08,343 --> 00:00:13,348
<i>I can't let anybody interrupt it</i>

4
00:00:13,431 --> 00:00:18,520
<i>I'm going to change</i>

5
00:00:26,986 --> 00:00:31,282
<i>The future that
the forbidden fruit foretells...</i>

6
00:00:31,366 --> 00:00:35,286
<i>I'm going to change</i>

7
00:00:35,370 --> 00:00:39,707
<i>The dream into reality</i>

8
00:00:42,252 --> 00:00:48,299
<i>The ending</i>

9
00:00:48,383 --> 00:00:51,594
<i>That everybody wants</i>

10
00:00:52,554 --> 00:00:54,847
<i>Within the spreading darkness</i>

11
00:00:54,931 --> 00:00:57,600
<i>I pledged our vow to the revolution</i>

12
00:00:57,684 --> 00:01:02,480
<i>I can't let anybody interrupt it</i>

13
00:01:02,647 --> 00:01:07,902
<i>Someday I'll show you</i>

14
00:01:07,986 --> 00:01:11,322
<i>A bright and ideal</i>

15
00:01:11,406 --> 00:01:17,287
<i>World</i>

16
00:01:25,962 --> 00:01:29,007
DECISION

17
00:01:39,976 --> 00:01:42,312
I relinquish ownership
of this notebook.

18
00:01:44,063 --> 00:01:46,649
Take care of Misa.

19
00:02:05,710 --> 00:02:07,170
<i>Mister Stalker...</i>

20
00:02:07,670 --> 00:02:10,381
<i>Hey, Mister Stalker,
where are you?</i>

21
00:02:11,299 --> 00:02:13,343
<i>Let's stop playing this game...</i>

22
00:02:14,677 --> 00:02:16,846
"Stalker?" What does this mean?

23
00:02:17,680 --> 00:02:19,223
Her attitude completely
changed all of a sudden...

24
00:02:26,689 --> 00:02:27,732
<i>Just as I thought.</i>

25
00:02:27,815 --> 00:02:31,402
<i>So as long as I have Ryuk's notebook,
even if I relinquish Rem's notebook,</i>

26
00:02:31,527 --> 00:02:34,322
<i>my memory of Rem doesn't disappear...</i>

27
00:02:34,989 --> 00:02:38,201
<i>But Rem, all these troubles are
happening to me because...</i>

28
00:02:38,284 --> 00:02:41,704
<i>you brought another notebook
to the Human World...</i>

29
00:02:43,456 --> 00:02:45,416
You really sure about this, Light?

30
00:02:46,084 --> 00:02:47,085
Yeah...

31
00:02:48,419 --> 00:02:51,589
I never thought that the notebook
I gave you

32
00:02:51,881 --> 00:02:54,008
would end up buried in the ground...

33
00:02:54,425 --> 00:02:58,304
Listen Ryuk, I'm just hiding it
there in the ground.

34
00:02:58,721 --> 00:03:01,474
I won't get rid of it until...

35
00:03:01,766 --> 00:03:04,268
the next time I say, "get rid of it."

36
00:03:05,019 --> 00:03:06,938
When I say it,
regardless of the context,

37
00:03:07,063 --> 00:03:10,483
assume it means I want to
get rid of the notebook.

38
00:03:11,192 --> 00:03:12,193
Got it...

39
00:03:13,069 --> 00:03:16,072
<i>Mister Stalker, this is illegal. Stop it.</i>

40
00:03:16,447 --> 00:03:18,324
<i>Please, Mister Stalker!</i>

41
00:03:18,700 --> 00:03:20,159
She's been acting like this

42
00:03:20,368 --> 00:03:22,245
ever since she passed out and
regained consciousness...

43
00:03:22,954 --> 00:03:26,332
Honestly. Does she think
she can act dumb like this?

44
00:03:26,874 --> 00:03:28,084
<i>Okay, I know.</i>

45
00:03:28,376 --> 00:03:31,129
<i>Could you at least take off
my blindfold?</i>

46
00:03:31,462 --> 00:03:33,548
<i>I really want to see
what you look like...</i>

47
00:03:35,633 --> 00:03:37,719
Mr. Matsuda...
Give Mr. Mogi a call.

48
00:03:37,927 --> 00:03:38,928
Huh?

49
00:03:39,262 --> 00:03:40,304
Oh...

50
00:03:41,681 --> 00:03:42,724
Here...

51
00:03:43,099 --> 00:03:45,685
When you apprehended Misa Amane,

52
00:03:45,768 --> 00:03:48,020
you told her that we suspect
that she's the Second Kira, didn't you?

53
00:03:48,563 --> 00:03:50,356
Yes... I did as you told me.

54
00:03:51,107 --> 00:03:53,192
I covered her eyes and mouth from
behind and told her so she could hear,

55
00:03:53,276 --> 00:03:57,363
"You're under arrest on suspicion
of being the Second Kira."

56
00:03:57,989 --> 00:03:59,532
She didn't seem to struggle

57
00:03:59,615 --> 00:04:01,159
even when I put handcuffs
and the eye mask on her.

58
00:04:01,284 --> 00:04:02,493
She seems to have given up.

59
00:04:03,828 --> 00:04:06,247
<i>I'll give you an autograph or
shake your hand...</i>

60
00:04:06,539 --> 00:04:09,250
<i>That's it! I'll give you
a kiss on the cheek!</i>

61
00:04:09,459 --> 00:04:12,086
<i>Please! I won't run away...</i>

62
00:04:12,920 --> 00:04:16,299
<i>We'd made so much progress with her.</i>

63
00:04:16,799 --> 00:04:18,968
<i>Why A9 she suddenly talking
about a stalker?</i>

64
00:04:21,095 --> 00:04:22,138
<i>Misa Amane.</i>

65
00:04:22,764 --> 00:04:26,350
What, Mister Stalker?
Are you planning to release me?

66
00:04:27,101 --> 00:04:29,103
<i>You were quiet before you fell asleep.</i>

67
00:04:29,228 --> 00:04:32,774
<i>You asked us to kill you.
Are you trying to give us trouble now?</i>

68
00:04:33,149 --> 00:04:34,984
What are you talking about?

69
00:04:35,359 --> 00:04:38,529
You're the one who knocked me out
and brought me here, aren't you?

70
00:04:38,696 --> 00:04:43,993
So what? Do you want to
play "investigation"? Is that it?

71
00:04:46,204 --> 00:04:48,956
Do you know why
you're tied up right now?

72
00:04:49,165 --> 00:04:51,793
<i>Why? Because I'm an idol?</i>

73
00:04:52,543 --> 00:04:56,672
You're the first stalker
who's ever gone this far.

74
00:04:57,965 --> 00:05:00,968
Hey?! Amane, quit fooling around!

75
00:05:02,261 --> 00:05:04,430
This is scary... W-What is this?

76
00:05:04,514 --> 00:05:08,434
I can't stand it anymore!
Let me go! Let me go...!

77
00:05:09,018 --> 00:05:11,020
Oh yeah... I have to go to
the bathroom again.

78
00:05:11,103 --> 00:05:13,189
I want to go to the bathroom. ...!

79
00:05:13,689 --> 00:05:18,277
<i>It's been only four minutes since
you last went. Please bear with it.</i>

80
00:05:18,694 --> 00:05:22,031
What's with that?!
That's the only way you'll untie me!

81
00:05:22,698 --> 00:05:27,703
You'll get to see me pee again.
Isn't that what you want? You pervert!

82
00:05:28,329 --> 00:05:30,540
I'm...a pervert?

83
00:05:31,791 --> 00:05:36,420
Amane, let's seriously talk more about
what happened before you went to sleep.

84
00:05:37,046 --> 00:05:40,716
Do you know Light Yagami?
Why did you approach him?

85
00:05:42,385 --> 00:05:45,054
Huh? There's no way
I wouldn't know my own boyfriend...

86
00:05:45,888 --> 00:05:47,890
<i>She was so tight-lipped
about it earlier,</i>

87
00:05:48,015 --> 00:05:50,101
<i>but now, she nonchalantly
says that he's her boyfriend?</i>

88
00:05:50,309 --> 00:05:51,602
What's going on?

89
00:05:54,730 --> 00:05:55,773
It's from Light.

90
00:05:57,400 --> 00:05:58,734
Please turn the AV off.

91
00:05:58,943 --> 00:05:59,944
<i>Yes.</i>

92
00:06:01,988 --> 00:06:07,451
Yes... Yes... Yes, I understand.
We're in room K2801.

93
00:06:07,952 --> 00:06:09,829
My son's coming here?

94
00:06:24,260 --> 00:06:26,762
Ryuzaki, I told you
over the phone, but...

95
00:06:27,930 --> 00:06:29,599
I think I might be Kira.

96
00:06:31,517 --> 00:06:34,896
That's impossible!
Light, what are you talking about?!

97
00:06:35,313 --> 00:06:37,565
What's wrong?! Tell me!

98
00:06:38,441 --> 00:06:40,943
<i>There's no proof that
Light Yagami is Kira,</i>

99
00:06:41,110 --> 00:06:44,363
<i>but... for him to say that
he may be Kira?</i>

100
00:06:45,031 --> 00:06:46,032
<i>It's all an act...</i>

101
00:06:46,532 --> 00:06:48,659
<i>It's not that you "might be" Kira,
but that you are Kira...</i>

102
00:06:49,493 --> 00:06:51,162
<i>What are you planning?</i>

103
00:06:52,121 --> 00:06:54,332
Dad, if Ryuzaki is L,

104
00:06:54,624 --> 00:06:57,001
then he is unquestionably
the best detective in the world.

105
00:06:57,460 --> 00:07:02,298
If L has decided that I am Kira.
Therefore, I must be.

106
00:07:02,798 --> 00:07:05,593
What are you talking about, Light?!

107
00:07:06,135 --> 00:07:08,346
The people Raye Penber,
the FBI Agent in Japan,

108
00:07:08,846 --> 00:07:11,724
was investigating before he died...

109
00:07:12,141 --> 00:07:14,602
The people that went to
Aoyama on May 22nd...

110
00:07:15,311 --> 00:07:18,564
And the first person
the alleged Second Kira, Misa,

111
00:07:18,648 --> 00:07:20,691
approached in the Kanto region...

112
00:07:21,525 --> 00:07:22,610
It's all me.

113
00:07:24,320 --> 00:07:28,032
If I were in L's place,
even I would say that I'm was Kira...

114
00:07:28,824 --> 00:07:34,455
See... I may be Kira.
I just might not know it.

115
00:07:35,164 --> 00:07:36,207
Light...

116
00:07:36,874 --> 00:07:39,877
<i>Isee. .. You're not conscious of it, huh?</i>

117
00:07:40,670 --> 00:07:43,506
I'm not sure of anything anymore...

118
00:07:44,256 --> 00:07:45,883
Even if I have no memory...

119
00:07:46,300 --> 00:07:50,846
there could be another me
who's killing people as I sleep.

120
00:07:51,347 --> 00:07:52,848
That would be impossible.

121
00:07:54,016 --> 00:07:55,434
What do you mean, Ryuzaki?

122
00:07:56,310 --> 00:07:58,104
Actually, there was a time when

123
00:07:58,187 --> 00:08:01,524
I put surveillance cameras
in your room for five straight days.

124
00:08:02,108 --> 00:08:03,150
Cameras?

125
00:08:03,693 --> 00:08:07,238
Yes. You slept normally at night...

126
00:08:08,531 --> 00:08:12,535
Criminals who were broadcasted,
that you didn't know about were dying.

127
00:08:13,119 --> 00:08:14,870
But I decided that,
even if you were Kira,

128
00:08:15,162 --> 00:08:20,042
you wouldn't give yourself
away on camera.

129
00:08:21,794 --> 00:08:24,422
"Won't give myself away," huh?

130
00:08:25,214 --> 00:08:27,216
That may be true...

131
00:08:27,842 --> 00:08:29,010
Well, up to a certain point,

132
00:08:29,093 --> 00:08:32,847
I believe that some
major criminals should die...

133
00:08:33,848 --> 00:08:38,227
I think that anyone who has
such thoughts could become Kira.

134
00:08:38,686 --> 00:08:41,564
Light! I believe the same thing!

135
00:08:42,023 --> 00:08:45,609
I've thought it would be better
if quite a few people were dead.

136
00:08:45,735 --> 00:08:49,739
But, even so,
we can't really kill people, right?

137
00:08:50,072 --> 00:08:53,784
Besides, criminals were dying
while you had no knowledge of them.

138
00:08:54,243 --> 00:08:56,662
The surveillance cameras proved that!

139
00:08:57,163 --> 00:08:58,289
N-No...

140
00:08:58,664 --> 00:09:00,583
We were short of investigators then

141
00:09:00,750 --> 00:09:02,334
and we only watched him
when he was at home...

142
00:09:02,877 --> 00:09:06,130
It's also not as if we were watching him
every hour during those five days...

143
00:09:06,756 --> 00:09:10,176
There might have been a way for him
to kill while he wasn't at home.

144
00:09:13,929 --> 00:09:17,308
<i>Is this all part of your plan,
Light Yagami?</i>

145
00:09:18,809 --> 00:09:23,397
<i>But if we restrain you for
a long period like Amane,</i>

146
00:09:24,231 --> 00:09:26,567
<i>and criminals
still continue to die...</i>

147
00:09:27,318 --> 00:09:30,613
<i>Is Yagami Light no longer
Kira at that point?</i>

148
00:09:31,989 --> 00:09:33,365
<i>Is this what you're aiming for?</i>

149
00:09:39,413 --> 00:09:43,542
I don't like where
this is going but...

150
00:09:44,585 --> 00:09:45,628
Fine.

151
00:09:47,171 --> 00:09:51,092
Light Yagami will be restrained
and placed under confinement.

152
00:09:51,634 --> 00:09:52,885
W-What. .?!

153
00:09:53,052 --> 00:09:55,387
You're going to detain. . .Light?

154
00:09:56,013 --> 00:09:58,557
If we're doing this,
we have to do this now.

155
00:09:59,350 --> 00:10:02,478
You will not be allowed to
leave my sight before then.

156
00:10:02,770 --> 00:10:06,315
T-This is crazy.
There's no way that my son is Kira...

157
00:10:06,690 --> 00:10:08,526
My son wouldn't...

158
00:10:08,609 --> 00:10:09,652
It's fine, Dad.

159
00:10:09,985 --> 00:10:11,028
Light...

160
00:10:11,320 --> 00:10:18,536
There's no way I'll be able to
pursue Kira if I suspect myself.

161
00:10:19,120 --> 00:10:23,082
In exchange, Ryuzaki,
until you decide that I'm not Kira

162
00:10:23,165 --> 00:10:24,875
or you agree that I'm not Kira,

163
00:10:25,126 --> 00:10:29,797
don't let me go, no matter what I say
or whatever condition I'm in.

164
00:10:30,923 --> 00:10:32,049
Understood...

165
00:10:32,508 --> 00:10:35,052
Mr. Yagami, are you able to
come up with an excuse

166
00:10:35,136 --> 00:10:38,097
for Light's absence for your family?

167
00:10:38,514 --> 00:10:40,015
Actually, please just do it.

168
00:10:40,558 --> 00:10:42,977
Well, I'm not too sure
I can so suddenly...

169
00:10:43,310 --> 00:10:45,563
But why does my son have to be
thrown into a prison?

170
00:10:45,771 --> 00:10:47,148
You're being stubborn, Dad.

171
00:10:47,565 --> 00:10:49,984
I can't be fully satisfied with myself
unless I do this.

172
00:10:51,193 --> 00:10:52,945
Are you serious, Light?

173
00:10:53,863 --> 00:10:57,199
Yeah. By taking away
my freedom,

174
00:10:57,658 --> 00:11:00,452
I'll be able to defeat the fear of
Kira that lies within me.

175
00:11:02,538 --> 00:11:04,123
Mr. Aizawa, I leave him to you.

176
00:11:04,957 --> 00:11:06,000
Yes...

177
00:11:30,691 --> 00:11:33,903
FIRST DAY OF CONFINEMENT

178
00:11:33,903 --> 00:11:35,529
<i>All that's left is to
get rid of the notebook.</i>

179
00:11:36,322 --> 00:11:38,699
Does this mean I won't
be able to eat apples again?

180
00:11:49,752 --> 00:11:50,753
Ryuzaki...

181
00:11:51,462 --> 00:11:54,089
Please take me off
of the investigation.

182
00:11:54,215 --> 00:11:55,341
Chief!

183
00:11:55,758 --> 00:11:59,720
We're holding my son as
a suspect in this case...

184
00:12:00,304 --> 00:12:02,389
I shouldn't be here.

185
00:12:03,390 --> 00:12:04,892
Regardless of whether
we should investigate him,

186
00:12:05,059 --> 00:12:07,311
when we were talking
about confining him,

187
00:12:07,394 --> 00:12:10,189
I let my personal feelings
get in the way...

188
00:12:11,148 --> 00:12:14,360
That's true.
Personal feelings shouldn't be involved.

189
00:12:15,027 --> 00:12:19,823
A-And, if my son really is Kira...

190
00:12:20,282 --> 00:12:22,618
I don't know what kind of
actions I may take.

191
00:12:23,077 --> 00:12:29,750
Yes. I can imagine that you would...
kill your son and then kill yourself.

192
00:12:31,126 --> 00:12:34,380
I agree that we shouldn't
have you here.

193
00:12:36,340 --> 00:12:37,341
Ryuzaki!

194
00:12:37,758 --> 00:12:39,468
Could you confine me as well?

195
00:12:40,552 --> 00:12:41,845
I'm calm now, but...

196
00:12:42,054 --> 00:12:44,682
I don't know what I'll do
when my feelings for my son...

197
00:12:45,349 --> 00:12:47,601
I thought you might
say something like that,

198
00:12:47,685 --> 00:12:49,770
so I've had Watari make arrangements.

199
00:12:52,439 --> 00:12:54,984
However, even though
you'll be under confinement...

200
00:12:55,401 --> 00:12:57,861
please keep your cell phone on as usual.

201
00:12:58,153 --> 00:13:00,948
Maintain regular contact with your family
and people from the outside.

202
00:13:02,074 --> 00:13:04,034
We won't tell Light about this.

203
00:13:04,410 --> 00:13:06,078
And if Light wants to talk to you

204
00:13:06,453 --> 00:13:09,081
we'll have you talk to him as if
you're right here, inside HQ.

205
00:13:10,082 --> 00:13:12,960
Also, we will give you
continuing updates

206
00:13:13,043 --> 00:13:15,879
of the what's going on
in the investigation.

207
00:13:18,007 --> 00:13:19,300
Is that okay?

208
00:13:20,426 --> 00:13:22,469
I am indebted to you, Ryuzaki...

209
00:13:24,763 --> 00:13:27,474
THIRD DAY OF CONFINEMENT

210
00:13:31,395 --> 00:13:34,481
<i>Mister Stalker,
I want to take a bath.</i>

211
00:13:35,149 --> 00:13:39,445
<i>You know Where I live, don't you?
Bring me a change of clothes...</i>

212
00:13:40,029 --> 00:13:42,156
This has gotten crazy...

213
00:13:42,489 --> 00:13:45,159
I feel so sorry for the Chief...

214
00:13:48,120 --> 00:13:49,455
<i>Ryuzaki, what's happening?</i>

215
00:13:49,830 --> 00:13:52,833
<i>Have any new criminals
been broadcast</i>

216
00:13:53,083 --> 00:13:55,085
<i>that Kira would target
in the last couple days?</i>

217
00:13:55,627 --> 00:13:57,921
<i>Did Kira kill anyone?</i>

218
00:14:00,007 --> 00:14:02,968
Quite a few criminals have
been broadcast,

219
00:14:03,218 --> 00:14:07,848
but since you've been detained,
none of them have been killed.

220
00:14:08,682 --> 00:14:11,352
No one's been killed? Really?

221
00:14:11,769 --> 00:14:12,811
<i>Yes.</i>

222
00:14:13,145 --> 00:14:17,274
I see... Maybe I am Kira...

223
00:14:17,858 --> 00:14:19,818
Oh man, I wanna eat an apple...

224
00:14:20,903 --> 00:14:22,154
<i>What's going on?</i>

225
00:14:23,030 --> 00:14:27,534
<i>I thought that the murders would continue
even with Light Yagami confined,</i>

226
00:14:28,202 --> 00:14:29,995
<i>but in reality,
they've completely stopped...</i>

227
00:14:31,205 --> 00:14:34,583
<i>It seemed like Light Yagami
wanted to be confined, but...</i>

228
00:14:35,125 --> 00:14:38,712
<i>this would mean that
Light Yagami is Kira...</i>

229
00:14:39,421 --> 00:14:43,425
<i>Now the question is whether
he was conscious of being Kira...</i>

230
00:14:44,385 --> 00:14:46,053
<i>If he is Kira..</i>

231
00:14:46,512 --> 00:14:48,305
<i>Does he think he can
get away with saying</i>

232
00:14:48,389 --> 00:14:50,349
<i>That he wasn't conscious
of what he was doing?</i>

233
00:14:51,892 --> 00:14:56,188
<i>It's not like Light Yagami. ..
No, it's not like Kira...</i>

234
00:14:58,357 --> 00:15:01,151
FIFTH DAY OF CONFINEMENT

235
00:15:02,403 --> 00:15:05,906
I can't take it, Light...
If I don't eat an apple soon...

236
00:15:06,407 --> 00:15:08,450
Anyway, I just have to
get through it...

237
00:15:08,784 --> 00:15:10,160
even if there's nothing to do...

238
00:15:10,411 --> 00:15:15,624
Mister Stalker, your video won't sell
if I'm just sitting...

239
00:15:19,628 --> 00:15:23,048
Mr. Yagami looks even worse
than Light or Amane..

240
00:15:23,841 --> 00:15:27,302
Of course. It's been five days
since Light's been imprisoned.

241
00:15:27,553 --> 00:15:31,432
During that time, not a single criminal
who's been broadcast has died.

242
00:15:32,015 --> 00:15:33,767
In times like this,
I suppose it's harder

243
00:15:33,851 --> 00:15:35,978
for the parents than
the suspects themselves...

244
00:15:36,562 --> 00:15:40,357
Especially since now, it's almost
definite that Light is Kira.

245
00:15:41,984 --> 00:15:42,985
Mr. Yagami.

246
00:15:43,277 --> 00:15:44,903
What is it? Is it good news?!

247
00:15:44,987 --> 00:15:46,029
Bad news?!

248
00:15:47,489 --> 00:15:50,284
Uh, no... Try not to work
yourself up too much...

249
00:15:51,076 --> 00:15:53,579
You won't accomplish anything
by mulling over things.

250
00:15:53,662 --> 00:15:55,038
The outcome will remain the same.

251
00:15:55,622 --> 00:15:58,292
Perhaps you should rest...

252
00:15:58,375 --> 00:16:00,586
<i>somewhere more comfortable.</i>

253
00:16:00,669 --> 00:16:01,795
Out of the question!

254
00:16:01,962 --> 00:16:04,548
There's no place anywhere
that would be relaxing in this situation.

255
00:16:05,299 --> 00:16:07,885
In the state I'm in now,
this is the best place for me.

256
00:16:08,969 --> 00:16:10,471
<i>No matter what the result,</i>

257
00:16:10,596 --> 00:16:13,098
<i>when I get out of here
I'll leave with my son!</i>

258
00:16:14,475 --> 00:16:15,642
I understand...

259
00:16:16,935 --> 00:16:19,730
SEVENTH DAY OF CONFINEMENT

260
00:16:28,363 --> 00:16:32,159
<i>Light, it's only been one week,
but you're looking worn out...</i>

261
00:16:32,993 --> 00:16:33,994
Are you all right?

262
00:16:38,665 --> 00:16:42,002
<i>I've come this far,
I think it's about time...</i>

263
00:16:48,383 --> 00:16:52,638
Yeah... I know I probably look
pretty bad in here, but...

264
00:16:53,138 --> 00:16:55,182
this pride, I'll just have to...

265
00:16:56,558 --> 00:16:57,601
get rid of it...

266
00:17:12,741 --> 00:17:13,825
Got it.

267
00:17:20,499 --> 00:17:21,542
Later.

268
00:17:32,302 --> 00:17:34,680
<i>What am I doing here?</i>

269
00:17:35,973 --> 00:17:37,015
Ryuzaki...

270
00:17:37,516 --> 00:17:41,478
<i>I know I agreed to be detained
and chose to do this...</i>

271
00:17:42,354 --> 00:17:46,316
<i>But now I just clearly realized that
doing this is meaningless!</i>

272
00:17:47,234 --> 00:17:49,027
<i>It's because I'm not Kira!</i>

273
00:17:49,319 --> 00:17:50,737
Get me out of here quickly!

274
00:17:53,240 --> 00:17:54,324
<i>I can't do that.</i>

275
00:17:54,408 --> 00:17:56,660
<i>We promised that no matter
what you said,</i>

276
00:17:56,743 --> 00:17:59,580
<i>I wouldn't let you out until we decided
on whether or not you were Kira.</i>

277
00:18:00,289 --> 00:18:02,457
There was something wrong
with me then!

278
00:18:03,041 --> 00:18:05,335
Do you really think that
Kira would be able

279
00:18:05,836 --> 00:18:07,963
to operate without being
conscious of it?

280
00:18:08,589 --> 00:18:11,758
I don't remember committing
Kira's crimes, so I'm not him!

281
00:18:12,759 --> 00:18:14,803
I also don't believe that

282
00:18:14,886 --> 00:18:17,431
Kira has been acting without
self-awareness all this time.

283
00:18:18,432 --> 00:18:21,977
But if you are him
everything matches up.

284
00:18:22,603 --> 00:18:26,648
As soon as you were detained,
murders by Kira stopped...

285
00:18:27,691 --> 00:18:29,901
Listen Ryuzaki, hear me out...

286
00:18:30,444 --> 00:18:34,323
I am not lying... I'm not Kira...

287
00:18:34,906 --> 00:18:37,451
I can only think
that I've been framed!

288
00:18:38,452 --> 00:18:40,746
<i>What's wrong. .. Light Yagami?</i>

289
00:18:40,829 --> 00:18:42,664
<i>What you're saying doesn't
make sense...</i>

290
00:18:42,956 --> 00:18:45,876
<i>But. . .for some reason it feels
like it's the truth...</i>

291
00:18:46,627 --> 00:18:49,171
Hurry and get me out of here.
We're wasting time!

292
00:18:49,463 --> 00:18:51,632
<i>No. I can't let you out.</i>

293
00:18:52,507 --> 00:18:55,010
Damn it... How did this happen?

294
00:18:55,552 --> 00:18:58,305
What's going on?
This isn't like Light...

295
00:18:58,847 --> 00:19:02,392
He's taking back what he said earlier.
It's not logical.

296
00:19:02,809 --> 00:19:07,105
We can't release him now
that the murders have stopped...

297
00:19:07,814 --> 00:19:09,816
Even I know that.

298
00:19:10,025 --> 00:19:12,069
Well, whatever anyone says...

299
00:19:12,152 --> 00:19:15,113
can't we just decide that
Light Yagami is Kira,

300
00:19:15,197 --> 00:19:17,199
and that the case is solved?

301
00:19:20,243 --> 00:19:22,871
FIFTEENTH DAY OF CONFINEMENT

302
00:19:22,871 --> 00:19:24,081
W-What's going on?

303
00:19:24,164 --> 00:19:28,460
Two weeks worth of criminals
were murdered all at once yesterday!

304
00:19:28,710 --> 00:19:31,088
Yeah... Kira is back.

305
00:19:31,088 --> 00:19:31,296
KIRA STRIKES AGAIN

306
00:19:31,463 --> 00:19:33,006
Did you tell the Chief?

307
00:19:33,632 --> 00:19:34,716
No, not yet...

308
00:19:36,385 --> 00:19:38,595
Chief, Kira has started killing again!

309
00:19:39,054 --> 00:19:40,055
What?!

310
00:19:40,138 --> 00:19:44,351
Kira was just taking a break.
He's started punishing criminals again!

311
00:19:44,559 --> 00:19:46,395
Is that true, Matsuda?!

312
00:19:47,062 --> 00:19:48,855
Then my son...

313
00:19:49,940 --> 00:19:52,526
I shouldn't be happy that
the murders have occurred, but...

314
00:19:52,859 --> 00:19:54,778
now, suspicion of my son will be...

315
00:19:55,278 --> 00:19:57,030
No, knowing Ryuzaki...

316
00:19:57,239 --> 00:19:58,740
He won't say he's completely
cleared just yet...

317
00:20:02,244 --> 00:20:04,371
Well then...
He's in the grey.

318
00:20:04,746 --> 00:20:06,123
Did you hear that, Chief?!

319
00:20:06,540 --> 00:20:08,834
<i>Yeah, he was pretty much
guilty up to now...</i>

320
00:20:09,251 --> 00:20:10,252
<i>Thank goodness...</i>

321
00:20:10,335 --> 00:20:13,088
It's probably a grey that's
one shade closer to being clear.

322
00:20:13,255 --> 00:20:14,381
Then I'll tell Light, too.

323
00:20:14,464 --> 00:20:17,592
Matsuda! I mean, Mr. Matsuda,
please stop.

324
00:20:18,093 --> 00:20:19,094
"M-Matsuda?"

325
00:20:19,511 --> 00:20:21,471
Don't tell Light.

326
00:20:22,222 --> 00:20:23,515
W-Why?

327
00:20:24,683 --> 00:20:25,684
Light.

328
00:20:26,309 --> 00:20:27,519
What is it, Ryuzaki?

329
00:20:28,437 --> 00:20:32,357
It's already been over two weeks.
There haven't been any new killings.

330
00:20:33,108 --> 00:20:36,069
Won't you just give up and
confess that you're Kira?

331
00:20:36,653 --> 00:20:38,155
<i>Don't say stupid things
like that, Ryuzaki.</i>

332
00:20:38,363 --> 00:20:39,573
You're wrong.

333
00:20:40,240 --> 00:20:44,119
I can understand why you deduced from
the investigation that I'm Kira,

334
00:20:44,202 --> 00:20:45,287
but it's a trap.

335
00:20:45,912 --> 00:20:50,542
I'm not Kira! Zoom in or something
and look at my eyes!

336
00:20:51,042 --> 00:20:53,587
Are these the eyes of
someone who's lying?

337
00:20:58,216 --> 00:21:01,803
Amane. .. You're really sure that
you don't know who Kira is, do you?

338
00:21:02,345 --> 00:21:05,974
<i>Huh? That again?
That's what I want to know!</i>

339
00:21:06,683 --> 00:21:08,643
<i>Kira is a hero of justice who</i>

340
00:21:08,727 --> 00:21:12,606
<i>punished the burglar who
killed my parents.</i>

341
00:21:18,862 --> 00:21:21,156
<i>I don't understand what's going on...</i>

342
00:21:22,157 --> 00:21:26,203
TO BE CONTINUED

343
00:21:26,578 --> 00:21:31,625
<i>I dreamed a dream
that no one could see,</i>

344
00:21:31,708 --> 00:21:37,005
<i>I threw away everything
that I didn't need</i>

345
00:21:37,380 --> 00:21:40,592
<i>I'm holding these feelings</i>

346
00:21:40,675 --> 00:21:46,014
<i>That I can't give up in my heart</i>

347
00:21:46,181 --> 00:21:52,437
<i>Even if my feet fall victim
to the shackles of sacrifice</i>

348
00:21:52,521 --> 00:21:57,025
<i>In between reality and my ideal</i>

349
00:21:57,818 --> 00:22:02,697
<i>I can't hold back
the flooding impulses</i>

350
00:22:02,864 --> 00:22:06,493
<i>Because I have a strong desire</i>

351
00:22:06,576 --> 00:22:10,163
<i>To accomplish</i>

352
00:22:10,747 --> 00:22:15,377
<i>[deceit] [fear] [vanity] [melancholy]</i>

353
00:22:15,669 --> 00:22:21,049
<i>I'm not weak enough to believe</i>

354
00:22:21,132 --> 00:22:26,096
<i>Any of these negative perceptions</i>

355
00:22:26,555 --> 00:22:31,893
<i>I'm a trickster
who doesn't know solitude</i>

356
00:22:36,189 --> 00:22:37,732
PREVIEW

357
00:22:37,732 --> 00:22:40,902
That's crazy! Wait, Dad!

358
00:22:41,361 --> 00:22:44,489
If I die here,
we'll never uncover the truth!

359
00:22:44,906 --> 00:22:46,992
Do you believe L over me?

360
00:22:47,367 --> 00:22:48,660
Dad!

361
00:22:48,660 --> 00:22:51,204
NEXT EPISODE: EXECUTION

